    "featureBullets": [
      "\u3010SPF 50+ 4-in-1 Formula\u3011: Our liquid foundation offers the ultimate convenience by seamlessly matching your natural skin tone. This multi-functional product acts as both foundation and concealer, providing instant hydration in just 30 seconds. With long-lasting, waterproof coverage that lasts a full 24 hours, it also boasts SPF 50+ protection against harmful UV rays.",
      "\u30104-in-1 Versatile Foundation\u3011This liquid foundation adapts to your skin tone, acting as a foundation, concealer, and moisturizer in one! Simplify your routine with long-lasting, waterproof coverage that keeps your complexion flawless for up to 24 hours.",
      "\u3010High-Quality Formula\u3011 More than just makeup, this foundation nourishes your skin within 30 seconds, delivering a refreshing, non-sticky feel and a healthy glow.Free from parabens, phthalates, and artificial fragrances, it\u2019s safe for all skin types.",
      "\u3010Light to Medium Coverage\u3011: Unveil the perfect fusion of skincare and makeup with our serum foundation. Infused with sunblock and enriched with broad spectrum SPF 50+, it delivers light-to-medium coverage to effectively conceal fine lines, wrinkles, and uneven texture, instantly elevating your complexion.",
      "\u3010Everyday Lifestyle Companion\u3011: Tailored for your active lifestyle, our sweat-proof foundation is ideal for daily wear, workouts, and dance classes. Free from parabens, phthalates, and artificial fragrances, it suits all skin types, ensuring you exude confidence for any occasion.",
      "\u3010Waterproof & Sweatproof\u3011 Ideal for daily wear and workouts, this sweatproof foundation suits all skin types, ensuring a flawless, natural appearance that lasts all day."
    ],
